text: Serdar Deniz (born 18 april 1969) is a Turkish alpine skier. He competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics.Titus is pretty well known for his role in Dirilis Ertugrul. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Alpine skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Turkish male alpine skiers Category: Olympic alpine skiers of Turkey
